      "popup": "<div style=\"max-width:300px;font-family:'Crimson Text',serif\"><h3 style=\"color:#90A4AE;margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px\">Southern Illinois / Shawnee Hills Karst</h3><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#78909C\">Karst in the Shawnee Hills and Chester Upland of southern Illinois. Sandstone and limestone shelters along the Mississippi bluffs — host to Modoc Rockshelter. This zone connects the Ozark karst to the Interior Low Plateaus across the Mississippi.</p><p style=\"font-size:11px;color:#607D8B\">Bedrock: Mississippian limestone and Aux Vase Sandstone</p></div>",
